   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Mumm_Co_Reims_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>G.H. MUMM &amp; Co.<lb/>REIMS<lb/>PETER ARNOLD MUMM<lb/>FRANKFURT a/M.<lb/> Reims,
                11th January 1872<lb/>Dear Messrs. L. Kniffler &amp; Co. Nagasaki!<lb/>We
                acknowledge receiving your esteemed <lb/>letter from 13th November of last year with
                the <lb/>sales calculation for the batch of wine consigned <lb/>at yours to the
                amount of $ 285 net<lb/>and we will check this and after finding <lb/>it correct we
                will pay this under the <lb/> usual conditions with the<lb/> ₤63.10.7 ex London at
                the rate of 4.5½<lb/>which your house in Yokohama has <lb/>transferred to
                us.<lb/>Although we are not particularly dissatisfied with <lb/>the result of the
                sale, we cannot quite resolve <lb/>to make a further shipment as a
                consignment,<lb/>but we are taking the liberty of offering <lb/>you our wines at a
                fixed price of <lb/>Fs[?] 4.50 per bottle, available here at the same <lb/>quality
                as the last shipment; this is an exceptional <lb/>offer price, which we are
                extending to you in order<lb/>to encourage you to take on this transaction &amp; to
                <lb/>turn our initiated business connection into a<lb/>permanent one. Our usual
                price for the quality</p>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Mumm_Co_Reims_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>you had is Fs 5.＂ per bottle <lb/>Franco[?] Reims + we hope that the discount<lb/>of
                50 <expan>Centimes</expan> per bottle will induce you to <lb/>indulge us by placing
                an order at a fixed <lb/>price. <lb/>We are looking forward to hearing from you and
                sign <lb/>Yours most respectfully <lb/>G. Hl. Mumm + Co.<lb/>⟨The revenue from your
                sales calculation is <lb/>ca. Fs 4.60. ⅌ per bottle Franco Reims, but we are against
                all <lb/>consignments, as we also told your boss at the time, <lb/>and only decided
                to make the now implemented shipment <lb/>on his advice, in order to demonstrate to
                you <lb/>what we can deliver. <lb/>M&amp;Co⟩</p>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Mumm_Co_Reims_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Mumm_Co_Reims_4.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>Messrs. L. Kniffler + Co.<lb/>Nagasaki<lb/>⟨1872.<lb/>Reims, 11th Jan. <lb/>G. H.
                Mumm+Co<lb/>Rec[eived]. March 21st<lb/>Ans[wered]. -⟩</p>
      </body>
